name: Womprat_(Togruta)

attributes.name: Skin color
values: Red and blue with white stripes

content:
Womprat was a male Togruta scavenger who lived during the Cold War. He had a shop on Carrick Station, where he bought and sold valuable materials and metals.
Womprat appears in the 2011 BioWare MMORPG Star Wars: The Old Republic as a Scavenging crew skill trainer on Carrick Station.
